    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/5f59aaa9ef1c3b59f88c41483cb22627.avif?t=1749788252\" width=610 height=546 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must save your niece, Nina, while escaping the merciless the Demon Bride You have 5 days to find her and escape before it’s too late. Will you survive or become her next victim?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/84c5ac73af662681230cc859c661c527.poster.avif?t=1749788252\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/84c5ac73af662681230cc859c661c527.webm?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/84c5ac73af662681230cc859c661c527.mp4?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/3c2547191abc16c745850e980695871c.webp?t=1749788252\" width=377 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hide and outsmart the Demon Bride. Watch your step! Every move counts to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/723905fcbfd6f4e74d00cfc3e86fa24e.webp?t=1749788252\" width=377 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mystery to help you escape. Use the items around you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/c19133804a4f6a6addc6f42ea931c6ad.poster.avif?t=1749788252\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/c19133804a4f6a6addc6f42ea931c6ad.webm?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/c19133804a4f6a6addc6f42ea931c6ad.mp4?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/ea289c535a297269bf56663dff3359b1.webp?t=1749788252\" width=377 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy retro graphics reminiscent of classic games, delivering a deep sense of nostalgia and a chilling horror atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/380b1ef11f059348355a224efb37fa32.webp?t=1749788252\" width=377 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a gripping horror atmosphere inspired by local Indonesian folklore and stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/de04c87f74c5d03cbf3e5dcdfc8421b2.poster.avif?t=1749788252\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/de04c87f74c5d03cbf3e5dcdfc8421b2.webm?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/de04c87f74c5d03cbf3e5dcdfc8421b2.mp4?t=1749788252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198970/extras/41f81412adabc595ca67668b22514cc2.webp?t=1749788252\" width=377 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from three characters, each with unique abilities and strategies. Can you save Nina and escape in time?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
